<plot>Barlow has acquired a large cattle herd and needs to drive the sheepmen off the range. When he has Jim Allen killed, Jim's twin brother Bob arrives and assumes his brother's identity. When Barlow slips revealing he knew about the murder, Bob knows who he's after and organizes the sheepmen. But they are in trouble as there is a traitor among the sheepmen.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?457662</url></doc>
